                    <span>"Don't Retire, Rewire," prepares the prospective retiree to think critically  about retirement before actually entering into it.  Retirement is often not what people expect.  This well-written book drives home the point that people approaching retirement age need to understand their drivers as they consider their "post-professional" life.  The case study approach is helpful, too.  I highly recommmend this book.</span>
                  
